solution.p:
Now, returning to our computation of the average velocity,
we find that

    AV_{[0.5, 0.5+h]} \amp  =  \frac{s(0.5+h) - s(0.5)}{(0.5+h) - 0.5}
    \amp  =  \frac{(12 - 16h - 16h^2) - (16 - 16(0.5)^2)}{0.5 + h - 0.5}
    \amp  =  \frac{12 - 16h - 16h^2 - 12}{h}
    \amp  =  \frac{-16h - 16h^2}{h}
    .
